author: dlydick
msg: Removed explicit disassembly of PC and opcode
in favor of using opcode_disassemble() to
show current machine state.
Removed STUB now that all opcodes are implemented.

author: dlydick
msg: Changed first parm of prototype for cfmsgs_atrmsg() to (const)

author: dlydick
msg: Added display of attribute via cfmsgs_atrmsg() after loading
a file, field, and method attribute.

author: dlydick
msg: Use renamed ATR_XXX_AI() and PTR_DST_XX_AI() macros
in support of easier identification of purpose.
Changed first parameter of cfmsgs_atrmsg() to (const).
Display exception_table_entry and exception_table structures.
Display exception_index_table structures.
Various corrections from using wrong data type macros.

author: dlydick
msg: Changed FILL_INFO_DUP[012] defines to new naming
method FILL_INFO_MEM_ALIGN[012] to be consistent
with the code changes.
Moved PTR_DST_XXX_AI() and PTR_XXX_AI() macros out
to 'attribute.h' for sharing with other areas of the
code.
Renamed some 'src' and 'dst' pointers to 'pev' and 'pevpma'
to be more descriptive as a pointer to element value
and pointer to element value pair, memory aligned,
respectively.
Renamed some 'src' and 'dst' anpointers to 'pn' and 'pnma'
to be more descriptive as a pointer to annotation and
pointer to annotation, memory aligned, respectively.
Renamed some 'src' and 'dst' pointers as 'pai' and 'paima'
or 'ppaima' to be more descriptive as a pointer to
attribute_info and [pointer to] pointer to attribute_info,
memory aligned, respectively.
